☕ Coffee Shop Guide

Waterlooville offers 39 excellent coffee shops, from well-known chains like Costa Coffee to independent local favorites. Whether you're after a quick espresso or a relaxing brunch spot, there's something for everyone.

What Makes a Great Coffee Shop?

  • ✓ Quality coffee and fresh ingredients
  • ✓ Friendly, knowledgeable staff
  • ✓ Comfortable seating
  • ✓ Good WiFi (for remote workers)
  • ✓ Clean facilities
  • ✓ Reasonable prices

Popular in Waterlooville:

  • ☕ Flat whites & cappuccinos
  • 🥐 Fresh pastries & cakes
  • 🥪 Breakfast & lunch options
  • 🥤 Smoothies & cold brew
  • 🍰 Afternoon tea
  • 🌱 Vegan & plant-based options
